    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable choice for a daily commuter. While the engine and transmission are solid, the car shows its age through several cosmetic imperfections, including some noticeable scratches on the passenger side, minor rock chips on the front bumper, and some thinning of the clear coat on the roof. The interior is generally clean but does show some wear on the driver's seat bolster. It has been well-maintained mechanically, though it is not in showroom condition.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean and retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and smoke-free; the upholstery is intact with only minor bolster wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car is solid, shifts smoothly, and all major electronics are fully functional. It is a dependable driver that offers a great balance of quality and value, perfect for someone looking for a reliable vehicle that has been looked after without the premium price of a showroom-perfect specimen.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this meticulously preserved masterpiece. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, maintained to exacting standards that ensure a showroom-fresh appearance and flawless mechanical performance. From the pristine interior to the mirror-like finish of the exterior, every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents an unrivaled opportunity to own a vehicle in truly superlative condition.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, it\u2019s hard to let this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience how smooth this beauty handles. It's been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, and looks just as stunning as the day it rolled off the lot. You won\u2019t find a single thing out of place\u2014it really is the definition of showroom ready. Come by for a coffee and a look, I promise you\u2019ll fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is an absolute pinnacle of the E92 chassis. This S65-powered M3 has been curated for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection. The high-revving V8 has undergone a comprehensive preventative overhaul, including BE Bearings with ARP hardware and updated throttle actuators with reinforced gears. The DCT logic has been optimized with a GTS flash, ensuring the dual-clutch engagement is as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. Suspension geometry is pinpoint accurate thanks to a recent corner-balancing on Ohlins dampers, and the subframe has been inspected with zero signs of fatigue. This isn't just a car; it's a meticulously calibrated instrument with a documented maintenance lineage that eliminates the typical S65 anxieties. If you understand compression ratios and oil shear stability, you know this is the one.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. First to see will buy. Firm price. No lowballs.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a vehicle; it is a time capsule of pure, unadulterated class. Imagine sliding into seats of supple, hand-stitched leather that still carries the faint, nostalgic aroma of a high-end boutique. The paintwork, a deep and lustrous midnight hue, reflects the world around it like a still mountain lake, while the engine\u2019s whisper-quiet idle promises a journey of effortless grace. Every dial and switch feels intentional, a testament to an era when craftsmanship was a point of pride. To own this car is to inherit a legacy of elegance; it is a rare chance to capture a masterpiece that has been cherished, preserved, and kept away from the ravages of time. It doesn't just drive; it glides, turning every mundane commute into a cinematic event.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle arrives in showroom condition, having been preserved with uncompromising attention to detail. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every aspect reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically perfect, this car offers the discerning driver an 'as-new' experience. A collector-grade opportunity for those who refuse to settle for anything less than the best.",
      "price": 48900.0,
